data.description: Spacious 5 bedroom, 4 full bath home is  located in the Eagle Canyon community of West Spanish.  This stucco exterior home is on a level .29 acre lot.  Laundry room with cabinets, gas log fireplace, central air conditioning.  Features a three car garage plus  additional RV parking area. List price includes washer, dryer, refrigerator.  Tile roof. Two storage sheds in the backyard stay.
